Wildrider looked at the tree, and started to kacle even louder, "Watch how
it's done Dead-End" he screamed, as he sent himself hurling towards the
tree, cutting his jets, so gravity was taking him down at high speeds. He
then shifted and transformed into his car mode. In the past he had ripped
through tanks, and now he had gravities momentum with him, as he headed
straight for the roots of Grounded, like a grey balistic missile, laughing
the whole way.
